data.description: This gorgeous townhome has two master suites, complete with attached bath and walk in closet. An incredible kitchen has tons of space to move around and includes stunning finishes such as wood look flooring, granite countertops and recessed lighting. All kitchen appliances are included! The open floor plan makes entertaining a breeze, For addition entertaining space, enjoy the covered back patio. The patio also features extra storage space!
